гичий.definition:
'Гичий' is a typical curse [word in] [Mongolia]
It is [literally] means 'bitch'
But often it can be used in males too.
гичий.example:
'Тэнэг Гичий!' = "[Stupid bitch]!"
'Лаларын хар гичий!' = "Fucking [black bitch]!"
'Будханд муу явдалтай гичий!' = "Budkhand you [sluty bitch]!"
